                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">作者对权力的剖析实在深刻，我常常能够对号入座，并开始认真审视自己的性格。原本以为自己的性格如何好，从这本书的分析看来，真的有许多需要反思和改正的地方。一本好书。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1126731305">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1126731305" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1126731305" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1126731305">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/137357053/">北极光</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-03-07</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">和我们时代的神经症人格比较阅读。
反思是我在阅读中着重于理解自己，应当把注意力向自身之外转移</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1126496445">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1126496445" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1126496445" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1126496445">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/yuch95603/">诗塔夫罗金</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2016-12-26</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">蛮有趣，关于暴力接近于生命力的想法和我很接近 </p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1121512406">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1121512406" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1121512406" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1121512406">有用</a>
                </span>
